I'd check out Cap's Paint & Body.  I've heard really good things about
them from co-workers that have gone to them.  I was gonna have them work
on my bus because it had alot of rust damage, but then I just went and
bought another bus :)

Check 'em out:
Cap's Paint & Body
2121 Orange
Signal Hill, CA
562-595-6035

